<p> </p></div><div style="margin:20px 3px 3px 3px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:3px;padding-left:7px;background-color:lightsteelblue">成績評価の方法</div><div style="margin:10px"><p><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Your teacher may adapt this based on student needs and progress.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Quizzes &amp; Assignments: 50%</span></span></p>
